title: Cardinal Ranjith returns from Vatican
body_lines: A group of Catholic Archbishops, including the Archbishop of Colombo, His Eminence Cardinal Malcolm Ranjith, arrived at the Katunayake International Airport in the morning.
They left for the Vatican on April 22 on a special invitation from Pope Francis.
They touched down at the BIA via Doha, Qatar at 9.12 am today. (T.K.G. Kapila)
